data.description: Discover this lovingly crafted 3 bd, 2 ba home, nestled in a friendly Nampa neighborhood. Spanning 1,400 sqft, it features a meticulously designed open floor plan that radiates warmth and care, from the countertops to the flooring. The LARGE backyard offers a serene retreat. Inside, the home boasts energy-efficient appliances, a cozy gas fireplace, and a covered patio for outdoor living. Recent updates include a brand-new water heater in 2022. Located close to downtown Nampa, shopping, and minutes from Lake Lowell. Neighborhood park and golf course also nearby. The tight-knit community welcomes with open arms, making it common to exchange greetings while enjoying a walk outside. This single-owner home has been meticulously maintained, with regular upkeep of the furnace and AC, ensuring a well-established, inviting outdoor space. Act quickly to make this uniquely personal retreat your own!  3D tour: https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=j9Xf1XSuY7i
